description: While presentation makes this pan-fried prosciutto-wrapped salmon feel fancy, the recipe is easy and affordable enough to have on weekly rotation.
name: Prosciutto-Wrapped Salmon With Quinoa Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Wrap each salmon fillet with a slice of prosciutto. Heat remaining oil in a large frying pan over medium heat. Add salmon and cook for 3 minutes on each side for medium rare or until cooked to your liking. Serve salmon with quinoa salad.
